DRAAD101 HOTFIX - Railway Deployment Fix
=========================================

Trigger timestamp: 1733330221000
Date: 2025-12-04 16:57:01 CET

Probleem:
- ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'fastapi'
- Railway service 'vibrant-emotion' crasht bij startup

Root Cause Analysis:
1. FastAPI staat WEL in requirements.txt
2. MAAR: Dockerfile CMD was 'python main.py' ipv uvicorn
3. Railway Root Directory mogelijk niet ingesteld op 'solver/'

Fixes Applied:
1. ✅ solver/railway.json toegevoegd (correct Railway config)
2. ✅ solver/Dockerfile CMD gewijzigd naar: uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port ${PORT:-8000}
3. ✅ Healthcheck fix: urllib ipv requests (dependency reduction)
4. ✅ Deze cache-bust trigger voor nieuwe Railway deployment

Verificatie Required:
- Railway dashboard → Service 'vibrant-emotion' → Settings → Root Directory moet zijn: solver
- Als niet ingesteld: handmatig instellen via Railway UI

Expected Result:
- Uvicorn start correct met Railway PORT variable
- FastAPI module wordt gevonden
- Service start succesvol op https://[service-url]
- Health endpoint bereikbaar: GET /health

Next Steps:
1. Check Railway deployment logs
2. Verify "Application startup complete" in logs
3. Test health endpoint: curl https://[railway-url]/health
4. Update Next.js SOLVER_SERVICE_URL environment variable
